title: Five banks in Lebanon held up by depositors demanding access to savings
description: Depositors held up at least five separate banks around Lebanon on Friday in an attempt to retrieve savings frozen in the banking system, a Lebanese army official told CNN.

title: Major fire breaks out at 42-story skyscraper in Changsha, China
description: A major fire broke out in a 42-story skyscraper in the central Chinese city of Changsha in Hunan province on Friday.

title: FedEx cuts sales forecast by half a billion dollars, warning of economy
description: FedEx shares plunged 21% in premarket trading Friday after it warned last Thursday that a slowing economy will cause it to fall $500 million short of its revenue target.

title: Chinese and Russian militaries share a potential weakness, new US report finds
description: China's military leaders share a potential weakness that has undermined their Russian counterparts in Ukraine and could hamper their ability to wage a similar war, according to a new report from the US National Defense University.

title: What Britain looked like the last time a monarch died
description: As the United Kingdom mourns Queen Elizabeth II, only a minority will remember first-hand what life was like the last time the country buried a monarch.
